  ('optometrist-moex-03468', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '視力檢查使用6公尺為標準的視力檢查表，其中標示為0.5的視標，在4公尺的地方看，所占的視角為：', '["2分角", "3分角", "10分角", "15分角"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03469', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '當視力表放置在10英尺處時，患者可以辨識的最低排是20/20。在20英尺遠的地方，他能看到的最低排 是？', '["20/60", "20/40", "20/20", "20/10"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03470', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '以角膜弧度儀（keratometer）測量角膜弧度，測得的角膜值（keratometer reading）為43.83 D，若角膜折 射係數當成1.3375，換算成角膜曲率半徑（radius of curvature），為下列何者？', '["7.50 mm", "7.60 mm", "7.70 mm", "7.80 mm"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03471', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '網膜鏡檢查時，距離受檢者眼前50 cm處投射平行光源於受測眼，其網膜反射光呈現逆動。則受檢者當 時的屈光狀態為：', '["超過2.00 D的遠視", "低於2.00 D的遠視", "超過2.00 D的近視", "低於2.00 D的近視"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03472', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '電腦自動驗光機使用紅外線掃描眼球的屈光狀態，理論上所測量到的度數比使用可見光測量到的度數：', '["紅外線測量到的近視度數較高，遠視度數較低", "紅外線測量到的近視度數較低，遠視度數較高", "紅外線測量到的近視度數與遠視度數都較高", "紅外線測量到的近視度數與遠視度數都較低"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03473', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '測量老花眼鏡度數時，何者錯誤？', '["一正視眼，調節幅度為2.0 D，希望看清楚眼前30公分的字，可配戴+2.00 D的老花眼鏡", "一近視-2.00 D眼睛，調節幅度為2.0 D，希望看清楚眼前30公分的字，可不須配戴老花眼鏡", "一遠視2.00 D眼睛，調節幅度為2.0 D，希望看清楚眼前30公分的字，須配戴+2.00 D老花眼鏡", "雙眼的調節幅度會比單眼調節幅度多0.5 D ~ 1.00 D"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
